address.streetAddress: Pinnacle Plan, Barefoot Lakes : The Pioneer Collection

location.fullValue: Pinnacle Plan, Barefoot Lakes : The Pioneer Collection

data.description:
The must have lifestyle of Barefoot Lakes! With easy access to Denver or Fort Collins via 25, the location is ideal. Barefoot Lakes is home to many trails, parks and of course lakes to enjoy summer fun. This nearly new west facing home is situated on on a cul-de-sac  and at the end of the street sits a neighborhood park and trails. The popular Lennar Evans model is an open floor plan that is spacious and inviting. From the moment you enter, you are greated with wide plank EVP flooring throughtout the main floor , and plenty of natural light from the abundance of windows. Go straight back to the great room which is perfect for watching the big game. Attached is the dining area and the large kitchen.Sliding glass doors from the kitchen make dining outside a breeze  Quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and beautiful white cabinetry make this kitchen a dream to cook in. There is a small office off the kitchen which also houses the large pantry. The first floor also has a powder room, and  built-in cubbies by the entrance from the garage. Upstairs, you have a large open loft perfect for gaming, TV or Homework. A large primary suite, has carpet, ceiling fan and en-suite. The primary bath has 2 separate sinks and a large walk in closet. The other 2 bedrooms are both good size and share a bathroom. The full hall bath also has double sinks and a separate area for showering making getting ready in the morning more efficient.  The basement is ready to be finished to fit all your future needs.
The backyard is fully fenced and ready to have your finishing touches. There are solar panels on the home to offset your electricty bills.
